<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="if-conj">if <strong><em>conj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪf/    美 /ɪf/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>如果：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If you lose something on a bus or train or in a station, please call Lost & Found at 202-962-1195.
如果你在公共汽车上、火车上或是车站丢失了什么东西，请拨打失物招领处电话202-962-1195。</p><footer>2014 全国</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>假如；万一：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>If I were you</strong>, I’d study finance. 
如果我是你，我就学金融。</p><footer> 北师大⑧ – 24</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We would have got wet all over if we hadn’t taken the umbrella. 
如果那时没带伞，我们全身就会湿透了。</p><footer>2013 重庆改</footer></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>是否：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Let me see if I can help you.
我看看能否帮助你。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.<strong>即使；虽然；尽管：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Brian rarely, if ever, goes to bed before 11:00 p.m.
布莱恩难得在晚上11点之前睡觉。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="if-so">if so</h3>
<p>1.<strong>如果是这样的话：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Have you ever been here? And if so how many times? 
你来过这儿吗？如果来过，来过几次呢？</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li><strong><em>_</em></strong>_we don't stop climate change, many animals and plants in the world will be gone.  （2018 北京）  </li>
<li>The climate here is quite pleasant, the temperature rarely, <strong><em>_</em></strong>_, reaching 30℃ in summer.  （2014 福建）<br />
A.if not<br />
B.if ever<br />
C.if any<br />
D.if so  </li>
<li>At fi rst he hated the new job but decided to give himself a few months to see <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ it got any better.  （2009 北京改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. If  2. B  3. if / whether  </p></div>